I條數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA.I. 係 an end,<br />\ndata mining, big data, ML, DL呢啲只係means嚟,<br />\n至於離目標(做到A.I.可以自我思想, 威脅人類地位)仲有幾遠, 冇人知!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8810cb68eb66970cb0b8a7e37602e07087fdc719","tid":307171,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十年前講緊BI, data mining, 依家係唔係入晒落AI條數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA.I. 係 an end,<br />\ndata mining, big data, ML, DL呢啲只係means嚟,<br />\n至於離目標(做到A.I.可以自我思想, 威脅人類地位)仲有幾遠, 冇人知!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nunspuervised learning <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd811674bd4aae0062739522924cbd8c3846925","tid":307171,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:17:42.000Z","msg":"有冇人有follow開李飛飛？"},{"pid":"2966d6bddb460e38d7d43f793954e7eaa86b2d41","tid":307171,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十年前講緊BI, data mining, 依家係唔係入晒落AI條數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nA.I. 係 an end,<br />\ndata mining, big data, ML, DL呢啲只係means嚟,<br />\n至於離目標(做到A.I.可以自我思想, 威脅人類地位)仲有幾遠, 冇人知!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nunspuervised learning <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nunsupervised learning都只係to discover patterns and make inferences from analyzing clusters of data; easy job, 唔complex. <br />\n<br />\n我其實係指<span style=\"color: green;\">the Master Algorithm</span> (our brain's neocortex holds a blueprint of this which is still unknown to human). 如果future A.I. 可以用呢佢嚟諗嘢, 你就驚喇! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://futurism.com/ray-kurzweil-theres-a-blueprint-for-the-master-algorithm-in-our-brains/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffuturism.com%2Fray-kurzweil-theres-a-blueprint-for-the-master-algorithm-in-our-brains%2F&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f06ba045\" target=\"_blank\">https://futurism.com/ray-kurzweil-theres-a-blueprint-for-the-master-algorithm-in-our-brains/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Master_Algorithm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FThe_Master_Algorithm&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=3272cc8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Master_Algorithm</a>"},{"pid":"3ee6831c9252f89d037c22eeb8d6b7696e4e639d","tid":307171,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"VR?"},{"pid":"29c329b96578f82b6544ae605e120f70d497cdcd","tid":307171,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:20:24.000Z","msg":"DL 入門卡係1080，有幾多學生afford到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034339a0e0a2d4f939af82ffc43175259321aef6","tid":307171,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:31:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DL 入門卡係1080，有幾多學生afford到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑"},{"pid":"18273579395f70c640a25dc9283b9d07951e0701","tid":307171,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"數碼暴龍或者洛克人"},{"pid":"63e88898ab9cdc85f73bd7f58e08fddb16800ea5","tid":307171,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"認真，保安問題"},{"pid":"41149a30491430b07bde2463e677b40bf547b4a5","tid":307171,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT